## ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture Overview

```
qldata
â”œâ”€â”€ api/            # Unified API layer (qd.data, qd.stream)
â”œâ”€â”€ adapters/       # Exchange-specific implementations
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ brokers/    # Binance, Bybit adapters
â”œâ”€â”€ models/         # Data models (Bar, Tick, OrderBook, etc.)
â”œâ”€â”€ transforms/     # Data cleaning and transformation
â”œâ”€â”€ validation/     # Data quality checks and rules
â”œâ”€â”€ resilience/     # Connection management, rate limiting
â”œâ”€â”€ monitoring/     # Metrics, alerts, health checks
â””â”€â”€ stores/         # Storage backends (Parquet, DuckDB)
```

